- Add CORS middleware to engine for cross-origin dashboard calls
- Fix Dockerfile EXPOSE and healthcheck to match engine port 3000
- Fix CIRoutingMonitor implicit any types breaking tsc
- Add CI workflow (engine build+test, dashboard build+typecheck)
- Remove demo-server.js and demo/ directory (mock server no longer needed)

